EN: This is an apocalyptic battle, we must be prepared.

ZH: 他们在预言的末日前几乎无法逃脱。
EN: They can hardly escape before the prophesied doomsday.

ZH: 神秘的末日预兆出现在天空中。
EN: Mysterious signs of the apocalypse appeared in the sky.

